item.description:
Simple Weblogic Learnings While working an internal engagement, I&rsquo;m tripping over Weblogic instances for days. Dipped into ysoserial plenty and ended up with some luck based off CVE-2020–14882 which was partially patched meaning I tweaked it and got an auth bypass but with zero privilege, so barely worth noting.
There were some backup servers running with exposed NFS shares though&hellip;
After digging through them and doing some googling on the folder structure, I&rsquo;m looking at is weblogic directories&hellip;
